                  "FRS"
                ],
                "institute": "2GERGSI"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The velocity filter SHIP(Separator for",
                " Heavy-Ion reaction Products) at GSI."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COIN",
                "SISD",
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The evaporated residues(ERs) were",
                "separated from the beam by the velocity filter SHIP and",
                "implanted into a position-sensitive 16 strip Si",
                "detector(focal-plane stop detector) which had an active",
                "area of 80*35 mm**2. Gamma rays were detected by a",
                "HP-Ge clover detector consisting of four crystals, each",
                " 50 mm in diameter and 70 mm in length, which were",
                "shaped and assembled to form a block of",
                " 102*102*70 mm**3. This detector was placed at a",
                "distance of 30 mm behind the stop detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Isomeric states in Th-214 and Th-213 were",
                "identified by means of gamma-rays measured in delayed",
                "coincidence with the implant evaporation residues."
              ]
            }
          ],
